      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "“It is a huge and daunting problem, but the Purdue way has always been to tackle problems, not hide from them,” Daniels wrote."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
